<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٨٠ ... سُورَةُ عَبَسَ ... آياتها ٤٢ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَبَسَ}</span> ... قَطَّبَ وَجْهَهُ، وَظهَرَ أَثَرُ التَّغَيُّرِ عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَتَوَلَّى}</span> ... أَعْرَضَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَن جَاءَهُ الْأَعْمَى}</span> ... لِأَجْلِ مَجِيءِ عَبْدِ اللهِ بْنِ أُمِّ مُكْتُومٍ - رضي الله عنه -.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَزَّكَّى}</span> ... يَتَطَهَّرُ مِنْ ذُنُوبِهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَصَدَّى}</span> ... تَتَعَرَّضُ لَهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَلَهَّى}</span> ... تَتَشَاغَلُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَلَّا}</span> ... لَيْسَ الأَمْرُ كَمَا فَعَلْتَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَفَرَةٍ}</span> ... مَلَائِكَةٍ كَتَبَةٍ يَقُومُونَ بِالسِّفَارَةِ بَيْنَ اللهِ وَخَلْقِهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَرَرَةٍ}</span> ... مُطِيعِينَ للهِ لَا يَعْصُونَهُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قُتِلَ الْإِنسَانُ}</span> ... لُعِنَ الكَافِرُ، وَعُذِّبَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَا أَكْفَرَهُ}</span> ... مَا أَشَدَّ كُفْرَهُ!<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نُّطْفَةٍ}</span> ... مَاءٍ قَلِيلٍ مَهِينٍ؛ وَهُوَ المَنِيُّ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَقَدَّرَهُ}</span> ... خَلَقَهُ أَطْوَارًا.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{السَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُ}</span> ... سَهَّلَ لَهُ طَرِيقَ خُرُوجِهِ مِنْ بَطْنِ أُمِّهِ، وَبَيَّنَ لَهُ طَرِيقَ الخَيْرِ وَالشَّرِّ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٢١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَأَقْبَرَهُ}</span> ... جَعَلَ لَهُ مَكَانًا يُقْبَرُ فِيهِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَنشَرَهُ}</span> ... أَحْيَاهُ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>